<td><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/thieunien/files/hi-tech/91115/huongdan/79ffd5a4d2a6574bc9b0b2f36e515864.jpg" alt="A2-Huong-dan-kiem-tra-pin-laptop-Windows-10-Battery-report-Windows-10.jpg" width="570" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<p class="PCaption"><em>&nbsp;Nhập v&agrave;o cửa sổ Command Prompt d&ograve;ng lệnh</em> <strong>powercfg /batteryreport /output &ldquo;C:\battery_report.html&rdquo;</strong>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
